					<![CDATA[
						 <p>While I personally don't really like esoteric object classes being used unless absolutely necessary, this one definitely deserves it. The CSS adds an extra touch that makes it even better. The concept of an interstellar viking ship is also really fascinating and I can definitely see the Foundation having a space force.</p> <p>Take all my +1s, good sir.</p> 
				 	]]>
