								<wikidot:authorUserId>3927912</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Not to be superficial but this CSS theme is God-tier to me and I had to fight my mouse from going to the upvote button instantly. I need just a bit more justification&#8230;</p> <p>I'm reading&#8230;</p> <p>Reading&#8230;</p> <p>&#8230;everything is in order here.</p> <blockquote> <p>It is believed that this is a result of the object impacting interstellar hydrogen at appreciable fractions of c.</p> </blockquote> <p>Damn. There it is. Amazing sentence.</p> <p>(The whole SCP is great.)</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
