					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Feedback from Gabriel Jade and The Great Hippo was very much appreciated. This is not the <strong>first</strong> new SCP set in the SOTM canon, that honor goes to an article on the Chinese wiki, actually. But I wanted to do something like this over here for a long time.</p> <p>Image is public domain and from here: <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Groa%27s_Incantation.jpg">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Groa%27s_Incantation.jpg</a></p> <p>Hope you enjoy it.</p> 
